(D.R.Hunt) M.Pell. in blue, and of 
<taxonomicName family="Commelinaceae" genus="T." kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="T. (Campelia) subsp. subg." order="Commelinales" pageId="21" pageNumber="32" rank="subGenus" species="crassula" subGenus="Campelia" subSpecies="subg.">T. subg. Campelia</taxonomicName>
